THE BRITISH LIBRARY'S APPROACH TO AACR2.
     
THE FORMAL COMMITMENT OF THE BRITISH LIBRARY TO AACR2 AND DEWEY 19 ENTAILED
SUBSTANTIAL CHANGES TO THE UK MARC FORMAT, THE BLAISE FILING RULES, AND A
VARIETY OF PRODUCTS PRODUCED FOR THE BRITISH LIBRARY ITSELF AND FOR OTHER
LIBRARIES, INCLUDING THE BRITISH NATIONAL BIBLIOGRAPHY. THE BRITISH LIBRARY
FILE CONVERSION INVOLVED NOT ONLY HEADINGS BUT ALSO ALGORITHMIC CONVERSION OF
THE DESCRIPTIVE CATALOGUING.
